# ==========================================================
# Proxy configuration for the scraper (server-side)
# ==========================================================
# The scraper accesses xvideos.com server-side. If it's blocked in your region,
# set a proxy URL to route requests through an accessible location.
# Examples:
#   PROXY_URL=http://user:pass@proxy.example.com:8080
#   PROXY_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8888
#
# Falls back to HTTPS_PROXY and HTTP_PROXY env vars if PROXY_URL is not set.
# PROXY_URL=

# ==========================================================
# Cloudflare Worker CDN Proxy (client-side media)
# ==========================================================
# Deploy the Cloudflare Worker (workers/cf-proxy-worker.js) to proxy video
# segments, HLS manifests, and thumbnails through Cloudflare's edge network.
# This is needed if the xvideos CDN domains are blocked in your country.
#
# Use: npx wrangler deploy
# Then set the Worker URL here:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_CF_WORKER_URL=
